    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Astroneer: Glitchwalkers》中前往Aeoluz星系探寻巨大的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Glitchwalkers” DLC是《Astroneer》的首个扩展包，提供了全新的探索区域，以及新的剧情、游戏玩法和有待解开的谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新的地平线正在召唤</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aeoluz，一颗全新的星球，也是我们迄今为止最大、最复杂的星球。新的生物群落和挑战正等待着所有勇敢或者愚蠢的异星探险家踏上这颗未知的星球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042220/extras/5ade99a73e5e54cfb0e1de561d0a47a6.poster.avif?t=1731719676\" width=500 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042220/extras/5ade99a73e5e54cfb0e1de561d0a47a6.webm?t=1731719676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042220/extras/5ade99a73e5e54cfb0e1de561d0a47a6.mp4?t=1731719676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>面对新的敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一名叛逃的异星探险家已侵入并控制了星系，威胁着任何可能会干扰这场前所未有的权力争夺的闯入者。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>风暴归来</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >太阳系中出现了故障风暴，玩家们必须防止自己遭受这些数字风暴的袭击，从而抓住机会完成任务。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新的科技树、模组，以及游戏玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探险家们必须利用训练，快速适应危险的新环境。搭配使用新旧科技，灵活应变，努力活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042220/extras/e43356a6ef264ba43e53c7037802138c.poster.avif?t=1731719676\" width=500 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042220/extras/e43356a6ef264ba43e53c7037802138c.webm?t=1731719676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042220/extras/e43356a6ef264ba43e53c7037802138c.mp4?t=1731719676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其他未公布的内容以游戏本体免费更新</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除扩展包外，所有玩家都可享受添加至《Astroneer》的剧情、游戏玩法及各种优化。</p>",
